metadata.name: Online — 01/33
metadata.description:
Error — 404 Not Found

The internet has connected human beings in ways that in the past would have been seen as magic. We are exposed to more information in one week than our ancestors would have been in a lifetime. This has given us much illumination, but has also given rise to great confusion. I don’t have any answers, but here’s a song I wrote called “Online”. You can get it.
